B-U-K-A-N S-A-U-D-A-R-I-K-U.

377
00:37:53,816 --> 00:37:55,550
Aku baru mendapat pesan darinya.

378
00:37:55,634 --> 00:37:56,860
Kami pasti berselisih jalan.

379
00:37:59,196 --> 00:38:01,532
(Dia menemukannya.)

