00:38:22,803 --> 00:38:25,639
Sepatu hak putih.

383
00:38:26,682 --> 00:38:30,978
Lalu di mana dia sekarang?

384
00:38:34,189 --> 00:38:35,608
Kau tidak tahu?

385
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:42,197
Dan pria itu memakai
topi dan masker?

386
00:38:42,573 --> 00:38:45,326
