517
00:47:28,307 --> 00:47:30,309
Katakan padaku sekarang!

518
00:47:37,900 --> 00:47:39,235
Jangan bunuh aku.

519
00:47:40,486 --> 00:47:43,239
- Tolong jangan.
- Apa?

520
00:47:43,906 --> 00:47:45,532
Saudaraku adalah...

521
