575
00:51:57,117 --> 00:51:58,535
Kami sangat menyesal.

576
00:51:59,036 --> 00:52:00,662
Andai kau memberi tahu kami...

577
00:52:00,746 --> 00:52:02,243
Aku terus mengatakannya

578
00:52:02,327 --> 00:52:04,082
